<ServiceLayout
  title="Group Candle Making Event"
  description="Group candle-making sessions for events and celebrations in Centerville, TN. Perfect for clubs, organizations, and special gatherings."
  price="$25-35 per person"
  duration="2 hours"
  location="Centerville, TN"
  keywords="group candle making, candle making party, group event, Centerville"
>
  <section slot="overview">
    <h2>Group Candle Making Event - Centerville, TN</h2>
    <p>Looking for a unique group activity? Host your event with our group candle-making experience! Perfect for clubs, organizations, celebrations, or any group gathering. Create custom candles together while bonding and having fun in a creative, welcoming atmosphere.</p>

    <h3>The Experience</h3>
    <p>This is candle making designed for groups. Your group will learn candle-making techniques, select scents, and pour beautiful custom candles to take home. Whether it's a book club, garden club, church group, or special celebration, this hands-on activity creates memorable moments and beautiful finished products.</p>

    <h3>What's Included</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>All candle-making materials and supplies</li>
      <li>Choice of container styles</li>
      <li>Wide selection of premium scents</li>
      <li>Expert instruction and guidance</li>
      <li>Step-by-step candle creation process</li>
      <li>Take-home your finished custom candle</li>
      <li>Option: Café refreshments available</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Perfect For</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Book clubs and social groups</li>
      <li>Church and community groups</li>
      <li>Birthday celebrations and parties</li>
      <li>Bachelorette party activities</li>
      <li>Club meetings with a creative twist</li>
      <li>Fundraising events and activities</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>How It Works</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Welcome and group introductions (10 minutes)</li>
      <li>Candle-making instruction and overview (15 minutes)</li>
      <li>Select containers and scents (15 minutes)</li>
      <li>Create and pour your candles (60 minutes)</li>
      <li>Finishing touches and group photos (20 minutes)</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Pricing & Duration</h3>
    <p>
      <strong>Price:</strong> $25-35 per person<br />
      <strong>Duration:</strong> 2 hours<br />
      <strong>Group Size:</strong> 6-25 people (larger groups available)<br />
      <strong>Skill Level:</strong> No experience needed
    </p>

    <div style="background: #e8f4f8; padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin: 2rem 0; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><strong>Book your group candle making event!</strong> Call (931) 729-8459 or email made@thelocalplacetn.com. Located at 111 South Public Square, Upstairs, Centerville, TN 37033.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

